title: #95: More Profiling of 13 Reasons Why
description:
The RCP team of Jim Clemente, Laura Richards and Lisa Zambetti return to discuss the middle episodes of 13 Reasons Why. Episode 4 follows Tyler, episode 5 focuses on Clay and episode 6 shows a Valentine's Day that spins out of control.
